cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a data-driven framework for monitoring manufacturing systems using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also discusses the challenges in achieving Industry 4.0, which involves the integration of cyber-physical systems, indicating a possible fit with cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
